        <abstract>
            <p>Sofya Kovalevsky not admitted to University in Berlin.</p> 
<p>Translating the four sheets CD sent. When will book [<hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>] be printed?</p> 
            <p>Alexander [Kovalevsky] has gone to the Red Sea to study corals.</p> 
<p>Will work on live <hi rend="italic">Scalpellum</hi> at Naples in spring.</p> 
            <p>Bemoans England’s Prussian sympathies. Paris will fall without bombardment.</p>
        </abstract>
